      <div class="single-article__language">
        <ul> <li><a class='fr wpml-ls-link'  href='javascript:void(0)'>fr </a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link en" href="https://voxeurop.eu/en/change-is-happening-now-in-europe/">en</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link de" href="https://voxeurop.eu/de/in-europa-findet-der-klimawandel-bereits-statt/">de</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link pt-pt" href="https://voxeurop.eu/pt-pt/a-alteracao-climatica-ja-esta-afetar-a-europa/">pt-pt</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link ro" href="https://voxeurop.eu/ro/schimbarile-climatice-au-loc-acum-in-europa/">ro</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link es" href="https://voxeurop.eu/es/el-cambio-climatico-ya-es-una-realidad-en-europa/">es</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link pl" href="https://voxeurop.eu/pl/zmiany-klimatu-dopadly-europe/">pl</a></li></ul>      </div>
