    <div class="Vcard_img">
      <img width="700" height="394" src="https://voxeurop.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/people_climate_change_osama_hajjaj_1.jpeg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://voxeurop.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/people_climate_change_osama_hajjaj_1.jpeg 700w, https://voxeurop.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/people_climate_change_osama_hajjaj_1-300x169.jpeg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" />      <div class="Vcard_tags">
        <a href="https://voxeurop.eu/fr/typology/report/"><span style="background-color: #1e32bb;" class="category_tag">Actualité</span></a>                  <a href="javascript:void(0);"><span
              class="sub_category_tag $custom_classes strap_line">Réchauffement planétaire</span></a>
              </div>
    </div>
    <div class="single-header__title text-center text-sm-left">
      <h1>Le changement climatique, c’est maintenant</h1>
      <p>Une série de cartes publiées par l’Agence européenne pour l&rsquo;environnement révèlent que l’Europe est exposée à des risques climatiques majeurs qui vont progressivement s’accentuer. </p>
      <div class="d-bloc my-2 publish_date_time">Publié le 4 mars 2020 à 23:03</div>    </div>
    <div class="single-header__author">
      <ul>
                  <li><a href="https://voxeurop.eu/fr/author/contact_5122976voxeurop-eu/" title="Articles par Emanuela Barbiroglio" class="author url fn" rel="author">Emanuela Barbiroglio</a>                      </li>
                              </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="single-article__language single-article__language__mobile">
      <ul> <li><a class='fr wpml-ls-link'  href='javascript:void(0)'>fr </a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link en" href="https://voxeurop.eu/en/change-is-happening-now-in-europe/">en</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link de" href="https://voxeurop.eu/de/in-europa-findet-der-klimawandel-bereits-statt/">de</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link pt-pt" href="https://voxeurop.eu/pt-pt/a-alteracao-climatica-ja-esta-afetar-a-europa/">pt-pt</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link ro" href="https://voxeurop.eu/ro/schimbarile-climatice-au-loc-acum-in-europa/">ro</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link es" href="https://voxeurop.eu/es/el-cambio-climatico-ya-es-una-realidad-en-europa/">es</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link pl" href="https://voxeurop.eu/pl/zmiany-klimatu-dopadly-europe/">pl</a></li></ul>      <div class="mobile-language-separator"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="single-header__image">
              <div class="single-header__image__container">
          <img width="700" height="394" src="https://voxeurop.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/people_climate_change_osama_hajjaj_1.jpeg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://voxeurop.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/people_climate_change_osama_hajjaj_1.jpeg 700w, https://voxeurop.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/people_climate_change_osama_hajjaj_1-300x169.jpeg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" />                      <a class="copyright_link" href="https://www.cartoonmovement.com/cartoon/25802">Osama Hajjaj | Cartoon Movement</a>
                  </div>
